      <p><span>1.2 when you use the Ops service, to ensure your normal using our service, maintain the normal operation of our service, improve and optimize our service experience, and ensure the security of your account, we will collect your device model, operating system, IP address, Ops software version, access networks, data type and status, network quality, equipment accelerator (such as gravity sensing devices), operation logs and service log information (such as your search, check the operation record in Ops, service information such as fault information, referral url) such as logging information, this information is to provide information service must collect basis.</span></p>
      <p><span>1.3 When you use the address book feature, we will irreversibly encrypt your address book information and only collect the encrypted information. The above information is sensitive information. Refusing to provide this information will only make you unable to use the above functions, but will not affect your normal use of other functions of Ops.</span></p>
      <p><span>1.4 When you use Ops search, we will collect your search record, reading record, recommendation record and visit time, interaction record, in order to provide you with more accurate and personalized service and content.</span></p>
      <p><span>1.5 When you use Ops voice input, voice to text conversion, and Ops Translation functions, we will collect your voice content, the voice or text information to be converted, and the text information to be translated, as the collection is necessary to achieve the above functions. After we process it in real time, we return the results to you, we don&#8217;t save your data.</span></p>
      <p><span>1.6 When you use Ops to communicate with other software or hardware, the provider of other software or hardware may, with your consent, obtain information that you actively disclose or transmit in Ops. You should fully understand the product functions and information protection policies of other software or hardware before choosing.</span></p>
      <p><span>1.7 When you use the Ops Video Dynamic feature, the video information you upload will be stored on our server, as storage is required to implement this feature. We store it in encrypted form, and you can delete any video you upload at any time. We will not provide such information to the public or use it for any purpose other than this function unless you choose to do so or comply with the requirements of relevant laws and regulations.</span></p>
      <p><span>1.8 When you use Ops favorites to store all kinds of information, the information will be uploaded and stored on our server, so that you can use the information when you log in Ops on other devices, which is necessary to implement the favorites function. We will store your information in encrypted form, and you can delete your information at any time. We will not provide such information to the public or use it for any purpose other than this function unless you choose to do so or comply with the requirements of relevant laws and regulations.</span></p>
      <p><span>1.9 You may enter gender, region, signature, address, invoice title, etc. in your personal information field, which will be uploaded and stored on our servers for you to use when you log in Ops on other devices. You can also modify, delete such information at any time.</span></p>
